f4chinese
=========

A vim plugin for vim first_char_search in chinese.

Author: yeshengzou@gmail.com<YeshengZou>

Other information in f4chinese.vim

INSTALL
-------

1. Copy f4chinese.vim f4chinese.py f4chinese_wubi.txt to your $VIM/plugin/ .
2. Make sure the `s:table` in f4chinese.vim is right.
3. Config your own map in f4chinese.vim if you like.
4. For windows user, may be you need to change the ENCODING in f4chinese.py

the f4chinese.py require Python 2.6.

USAGE
-----

In normal mode, press <M-f>, then type the first_char, after <Enter>
the cursor will get the position.

<M-;> will search the next one in this line.

